This plugin provides a high-performance, low-latency Deep Packet Inspection (DPI) engine 
for OPNsense, specifically designed for industrial environments and Zero Trust security architectures.

Key Features:
- Deep Packet Inspection with application-layer analysis
- Zero Trust principles: all traffic is untrusted until verified
- Industrial protocol support (Modbus, DNP3, OPC UA)
- Optimized for low-latency OT environments (SCADA, PLC systems)
- Real-time threat detection and malware analysis
- Advanced behavioral anomaly detection
- SQL injection, XSS, and command injection detection
- Cryptocurrency mining detection
- Data exfiltration monitoring
- Industrial-specific threat patterns
- Performance monitoring with microsecond latency tracking
- Comprehensive logging and alerting system
- Web-based management interface
- Custom signature support
- Automatic threat intelligence updates

Industrial Environment Support (F-06):
- Microsecond-level latency monitoring
- SCADA and PLC protocol awareness
- Emergency response capabilities
- Production-safe operation modes
- Real-time performance metrics

Deep Packet Inspection (F-08):
- Application payload analysis
- Multi-protocol support (HTTP/HTTPS, FTP, SMTP, DNS)
- Pattern matching engine
- Behavioral analysis
- Zero-day heuristics
- Archive extraction and scanning

The plugin is fully implemented in Python for optimal performance and flexibility,
with a focus on maintaining sub-millisecond latency for critical industrial systems
while providing comprehensive security coverage under Zero Trust principles.

